{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XpcsxvR2hCXcfjGNGn1zxC","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the complete output from both sheets.\n\n---\n\n## Top 3 Opportunities Sheet (`A1:D5`)\n\nThe sheet has 4 columns and 5 rows (row 1 = headers, rows 2–4 = data, row 5 appears empty). No merge metadata was returned by xlsx, but the layout is:\n\n| Cell | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| B1 | Opportunity |\n| C1 | Explanation |\n| D1 | Estimated Annual Savings (USD) |\n| A2 | Opportunity 1 |\n| B2 | Renegotiate Salesforce UK Enterprise Contract |\n| C2 | 3-bullet explanation (Salesforce UK at $3.1M / 39.5% of spend; 15% savings via multi-year renegotiation; $465K annually) |\n| D2 | 465000 (numeric) |\n| A3 | Opportunity 2 |\n| B3 | Terminate Low-Value Long-tail Vendors |\n| C3 | 3-bullet explanation (267 Terminate-rated vendors / $1.55M; cancel Score-1 SaaS immediately; $232K within 90 days) |\n| D3 | 232000 (numeric) |\n| A4 | Opportunity 3 |\n| B4 | Consolidate Co-working and Office Space Portfolio |\n| C4 | 3-bullet explanation ($827K fragmented co-working spend; consolidate to 1–2 providers; $124K annually) |\n| D4 | 124000 (numeric) |\n\nColumn A is unlabeled in row 1 (no A1 cell value). Row 5 is empty. D2/D3/D4 are stored as plain numbers (no currency formatting visible in the raw data).\n\n---\n\n## Vendor Analysis Assessment — First 20 Rows\n\n**Headers (Row 1):**\n`Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\n\n**Data rows 2–20 (alphabetical, starting from \"(Blank)\"):**\n\n| # | Vendor Name | Dept | Cost (USD) | Suggestion |\n|---|-------------|------|-----------|------------|\n| 1 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Terminate |\n| 2 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Consolidate |\n| 3 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Consolidate |\n| 4 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Terminate |\n| 5 | 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | Terminate |\n| 6 | Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Consolidate |\n| 7 | Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | Consolidate |\n| 8 | Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Terminate |\n| 9 | Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Terminate |\n| 10 | Adobe Systems Software | SaaS | 3,928.65 | Terminate |\n| 11 | Advena | G&A | 153.89 | Terminate |\n| 12 | Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | G&A | 124,661.46 | Optimize |\n| 13 | Ag Grid Ltd | Engineering | 2,653.27 | Terminate |\n| 14 | Agram Life Osiguranje D.O.O. | G&A | 24,952.20 | Terminate |\n| 15 | Aha! Labs Inc | Product | 3,689.33 | Consolidate |\n| 16 | Akton D.O.O. | Facilities | 3,253.58 | Terminate |\n| 17 | Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited | HR | 6,098.63 | Optimize |\n| 18 | Allianz Wa | G&A | 970.71 | Consolidate |\n| 19 | Amazon (Aus) | G&A | 233.31 | Terminate |\n\n**Notable observations:**\n- The `DERIVED-Spend Category` column (column F) is empty for all rows in this range — it appears to be a column reserved for derived/calculated data that has not yet been populated.\n- Cost values are stored as raw floating-point numbers (not formatted as currency in the raw data).\n- The sheet is sorted alphabetically by vendor name."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aaca6e088836bf3e6 (use SendMessage with to: 'aaca6e088836bf3e6' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 13163\ntool_uses: 3\nduration_ms: 32923</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f6caffc-46c6-4fac-93a8-e3128f1add7b","uuid":"02dc33d5-4ed6-4232-ac91-439d9f4fe5ee","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:31:49.360Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at: C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nUse a Node.js script to:\n1. Read the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet and return ALL cell data (addresses, values, and any formatting/merge info visible)\n2. Read the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - return the first 20 rows with all columns\n\nRun the script using node in bash. Here is a starter script approach:\n\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst workbook = XLSX.readFile('C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx');\n\n// Top 3 Opportunities sheet\nconst sheet1 = workbook.Sheets['Top 3 Opportunities'];\nconsole.log('=== Top 3 Opportunities Sheet ===');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(sheet1, null, 2));\n\n// Vendor Analysis Assessment sheet  \nconst sheet2 = workbook.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nconsole.log('\\n=== Vendor Analysis Assessment (first rows) ===');\nconst data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(sheet2, {header:1, range: 0, defval: ''});\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(data.slice(0, 20), null, 2));\n```\n\nSave this as a temp file and run it. Return the complete output.","agentId":"aaca6e088836bf3e6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the complete output from both sheets.\n\n---\n\n## Top 3 Opportunities Sheet (`A1:D5`)\n\nThe sheet has 4 columns and 5 rows (row 1 = headers, rows 2–4 = data, row 5 appears empty). No merge metadata was returned by xlsx, but the layout is:\n\n| Cell | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| B1 | Opportunity |\n| C1 | Explanation |\n| D1 | Estimated Annual Savings (USD) |\n| A2 | Opportunity 1 |\n| B2 | Renegotiate Salesforce UK Enterprise Contract |\n| C2 | 3-bullet explanation (Salesforce UK at $3.1M / 39.5% of spend; 15% savings via multi-year renegotiation; $465K annually) |\n| D2 | 465000 (numeric) |\n| A3 | Opportunity 2 |\n| B3 | Terminate Low-Value Long-tail Vendors |\n| C3 | 3-bullet explanation (267 Terminate-rated vendors / $1.55M; cancel Score-1 SaaS immediately; $232K within 90 days) |\n| D3 | 232000 (numeric) |\n| A4 | Opportunity 3 |\n| B4 | Consolidate Co-working and Office Space Portfolio |\n| C4 | 3-bullet explanation ($827K fragmented co-working spend; consolidate to 1–2 providers; $124K annually) |\n| D4 | 124000 (numeric) |\n\nColumn A is unlabeled in row 1 (no A1 cell value). Row 5 is empty. D2/D3/D4 are stored as plain numbers (no currency formatting visible in the raw data).\n\n---\n\n## Vendor Analysis Assessment — First 20 Rows\n\n**Headers (Row 1):**\n`Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\n\n**Data rows 2–20 (alphabetical, starting from \"(Blank)\"):**\n\n| # | Vendor Name | Dept | Cost (USD) | Suggestion |\n|---|-------------|------|-----------|------------|\n| 1 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Terminate |\n| 2 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Consolidate |\n| 3 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Consolidate |\n| 4 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Terminate |\n| 5 | 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | Terminate |\n| 6 | Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Consolidate |\n| 7 | Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | Consolidate |\n| 8 | Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Terminate |\n| 9 | Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Terminate |\n| 10 | Adobe Systems Software | SaaS | 3,928.65 | Terminate |\n| 11 | Advena | G&A | 153.89 | Terminate |\n| 12 | Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | G&A | 124,661.46 | Optimize |\n| 13 | Ag Grid Ltd | Engineering | 2,653.27 | Terminate |\n| 14 | Agram Life Osiguranje D.O.O. | G&A | 24,952.20 | Terminate |\n| 15 | Aha! Labs Inc | Product | 3,689.33 | Consolidate |\n| 16 | Akton D.O.O. | Facilities | 3,253.58 | Terminate |\n| 17 | Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited | HR | 6,098.63 | Optimize |\n| 18 | Allianz Wa | G&A | 970.71 | Consolidate |\n| 19 | Amazon (Aus) | G&A | 233.31 | Terminate |\n\n**Notable observations:**\n- The `DERIVED-Spend Category` column (column F) is empty for all rows in this range — it appears to be a column reserved for derived/calculated data that has not yet been populated.\n- Cost values are stored as raw floating-point numbers (not formatted as currency in the raw data).\n- The sheet is sorted alphabetically by vendor name."}],"totalDurationMs":32923,"totalTokens":13163,"totalToolUseCount":3,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2602,"cache_read_input_tokens":9381,"output_tokens":1179,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2602},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
